7c restructed enable / setup\",\"stderr\":\"\",\"interrupted\":false,\"isImage\":false,\"noOutputExpected\":false},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"52d58789-485e-40d1-9497-b2393bc5e9f5\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"96c1f5ca-ea15-448b-8d74-901a5c585d74\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli_worktree1\",\"sessionId\":\"460b7f6a-8219-478a-b1bd-4df8d5db96a5\",\"version\":\"2.1.72\",\"gitBranch\":\"soph/improve-enable\",\"slug\":\"lucky-strolling-origami\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01PQ5xoVQ2DmvZTJEh9tQi9v\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Here's an overview of the changes on this branch:\\n\\n## Overview: Redesigned CLI Setup Flow\\n\\n### New command: `entire configure`\\n\\nA new command that handles both first-time setup and ongoing agent management:\\n\\n- **Fresh repo** (no `.entire/`): Runs the full setup flow — agent detection/selection, hook installation, settings creation, telemetry prompt\\n- **Already configured**: Shows currently enabled agents and presents a multi-select to enable more. Already-installed agents can't be deselected (validation directs users to `entire disable --uninstall` for removal)\\n- Supports `--agent <name>` for non-interactive use\\n\\n### Changed: `entire` (root command, no args)\\n\\n- **Fresh repo**: Now starts the configure flow automatically instead of showing help\\n- **Already configured**: Shows help (unchanged)\\n\\n### Changed: `entire enable`\\n\\n- **Fresh repo**: Runs the full configure flow (same as before)\\n- **Already enabled**: Shows status with installed agents and directs to `entire configure` for changes\\n- **Disabled → re-enabled**: Flips the flag and shows the same agent status info\\n- `--agent` flag still works for targeted agent setup regardless of state\\n\\n### Bug fix: `entire disable` → `entire enable` cycle\\n\\n`runEnable` now writes to `settings.local.json` by default (matching `runDisable`), so re-enabling correctly overrides a local disable. Previously it wrote to `settings.json` while the disable lived in `settings.local.json`, meaning the local override kept winning and enable never actually took effect.\\n\\n### Files changed\\n\\n| File | Change |\\n|---|---|\\n| `settings/settings.go` | Added `IsSetUpAny()` — checks both `settings.json` and `settings.local.json` |\\n| `root.go` | Root command detects fresh repos and starts configure flow |\\n| `setup.go` | New `entire configure` command, `runSetupFlow()`, `runAddAgents()`, `printEnabledStatus()` helper; modified `enable` behavior; fixed `runEnable` to write to local settings |\\n| `setup_test.go` | Updated `runEnable` call sites for new signature |\\n\\n### Terminology\\n\\n- \\\"current project\\\" → \\\"current repository\\\" throughout\\n- Help text points to `entire configure` instead of `entire enable`\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":114,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":112395,\"output_tokens\":538,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":114,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYufV2BvBni9B8wEuQjw7\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"ff483120-aa3c-45cc-8a5d-021746de203d\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-10T15:50:00.324Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"ff483120-aa3c-45cc-8a5d-021746de203d\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli_worktree1\",\"sessionId\":\"460b7f6a-8219-478a-b1bd-4df8d5db96a5\",\"version\":\"2.1.72\",\"gitBranch\":\"soph/improve-enable\",\"slug\":\"lucky-strolling-origami\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go hooks clau